VOLVO RTI (MMM+) - HDD EUROPE - 2013


Previous Volvo Part number: 31357745
Volvo Part number: 31396119

Model compatibility:
Compatible with all:
C30         MY 2007 - 2012
C70         MY 2007 - 2013
S40         MY 2007 - 2012
V50         MY 2007 - 2012
XC90        MY 2006 -

This Volvo GPS map covers 9 677 198 kilometers of roads, including motorways and local roads and has 3 719 053 Points Of Interest to give you the best driving experience with your Volvo RTI (MMM+) - HDD navigation system.

Be informed of changes on the road network including new motorway junctions, turn restrictions, roundabouts, one-way roads or new street names and make your itineraries faster and more reliable.

The integrated Traffic Messaging Channel (TMC) delivers live traffic information and the choice of alternative routes. In this Volvo map update, TMC codes have been renewed and are available in Belgium, Czech Republic, Denmark, France, Germany, Italy, Netherlands, Norway, Spain, Sweden, Switzerland, United Kingdom.

This product covers Europe.

Detailed coverage : Albania, Austria, Belgium, Bosnia Herzegovina, Bulgaria, Croatia, Czech Republic, Denmark, Estonia, Finland, France, Germany, Greece, Hungary, Ireland, Italy, Latvia, Lithuania, Luxembourg, Macedonia (F.Y.R.O.M), Montenegro, Netherlands, Norway, Poland, Portugal, Romania, Serbia, Slovak Republic, Slovenia, Spain, Sweden, Switzerland, United Kingdom
